title: Beef wontons
ingredients: ['1 medium head cabbage, finely shredded', '1 (300g) packet beansprouts', '3 stalks celery, chopped', '2 spring onions, chopped', '400g (14 oz) prawns - peeled, deveined and coarsely chopped', '500g (1 1/4 lb) lean minced beef', '3 tablespoons oyster sauce', '5 tablespoons soy sauce', '2 cloves garlic, minced', '1 packet wonton skins (wrappers)', '250ml (8 fl oz) vegetable oil']
